            <div id="content">
                <div id="pageTitle">Avoiding Inappropriate Questions</div>
                       
                    <div id="ContentText" class="pagesubtext animate">As the face of <strong><b>Test My Interview</b></strong>, it is important for you to  avoid asking inappropriate questions during the interview while still getting to the root of the concern behind the question.Â The table below gives you a few examples of how to ask these questions appropriately.</div>
